{
  "texts": [
    "MPT jumps from 40.9% (7B) to 48.2% (30B) accuracy.",
    "Alpaca even drops from 46.4% (7B) to 45.5% (30B).",
    "However, a few other competitive models got available.",
    "Falcon 40B instruct achieved 55.5% accuracy, the same as IBM's Dromedary with 65B parameters and GPTQ [54].",
    "Allen AI's Tulu 30B performed only mediocre with 49.1% compared to Caldera AI's Lazarus 30B that achieved 64% and therefore outperformed ChatGPT (60.9%)."
  ]
}